BorderContainer
public abstract class AbstractDojoComplexPanel
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.ComplexPanel
implements DojoPanel, HasAdaptiveSize

This class facilitates the integration of dojo's layouts by conveniently overriding the ComplexPanel methods. It only accepts other DojoPanel, but subclasses can be more restrictive if needed (most dojo layouts only accepts ContentPanel as a child).

Author:
rdunklau
